          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"openrouter-playground\">OpenRouter playground</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Pick a Hugging Face dataset, a list of OpenRouter model ids, and an <code>N</code>.\nClick <strong>Run</strong> to fan out N rows \u00d7 M models. Results land in\n<code>results/&lt;dataset_slug&gt;/&lt;timestamp&gt;__&lt;model&gt;__nN.parquet</code> with a JSON\nsidecar of run metadata. Identical calls are cached on disk.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Requires <code>OPENROUTER_API_KEY</code> in your environment.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
